    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" subtype="diplomatic" ana="b1">
                <p>ΗΜΟΝΑΡΧΙΚΗΕΞΟΥϹΙΑ <lb/> 
                    ΕΛΕΗϹΗΤΑΠΙΝΟΥϹ <lb/>
                    ΚΑΙΕΛΑΙΕΙΝΟΥϹΚΑΜΟ <lb/> 
                    ΤΑϹΕΝΤΩΔΕΤΩΟΙΚΩ</p>
            </div>
            <div type="edition" subtype="transcription" ana="b1">
                <p>Ἡ μοναρχικὴ ἐξουσία <lb/> 
                    ἐλεήσῃ ταπ<supplied reason="omitted">ε</supplied>ινοὺς <lb/>
                    καὶ ἐλ<supplied reason="omitted">ε</supplied>εινοὺς καμό<supplied reason="omitted">ν</supplied> <lb/> τας ἐν τῷδε τῷ οἴκῳ </p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>May the sovereign power have mercy upon the lowly and miserable men who have
                    labored in this house.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p>A somewhat different translation of the last phrase of the inscription, ἐν τῷδε
                    τῷ οἴκῳ, could be “in this room” rather than “in this house,” with a specific
                    reference to the laying of the mosaic floor in the triclinium of the villa</p>
            </div>
        </body>
